This is my Xmonad configuration with xmobar and some other stuff.

To install and use it, first install from you package manager this softwares:
uzbl-browser (or uzbl in ubuntu)
xmonad
xmobar
dmenu
feh
xscreensaver

For installation:
wget
make



Install configuration like this:
make -f <(wget https://raw.github.com/metal3d/xmonad-config/master/Makefile -O -)

